OL,3,CUK Athletics boss defends shock
OL,4,Cdecision to include CJ Ujah in GB
OL,5,Crelay squad
OL,7,FHe said: "In the past, this sport
OL,8,Fhasn't been very good at moving on and
OL,9,Ffocusing on the future, so absolutely
OL,10,FI think it's difficult and really
OL,11,Fchallenging for everyone involved, but
OL,12,Fwe have to stick by the World
OL,13,FAthletics rules."
OL,15,FMr Buckner said there has been no
OL,16,Flegal pressure to include Mr Ujah, but
OL,17,Fwhen asked whether he was comfortable
OL,18,Fwith the decision on ethical grounds,
OL,19,Fhe was non-committal.
