OL,3,CUK Athletics boss defends shock
OL,4,Cdecision to include CJ Ujah in GB
OL,5,Crelay squad
OL,7,F"That is a very hard question, and I
OL,8,Fwould say it's a difficult judgment
OL,9,Fcall to make, and I'm not prepared to
OL,10,Fgo one way or the other on that," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FRichard Kilty, who was part of the
OL,14,FTokyo silver winning team and is also
OL,15,Fin the current squad, told ITV News
OL,16,Fafter Mr Ujah's failed doping test that
OL,18,FAt the time, he said he'd never
OL,19,Fforgive Mr Ujah as his actions had
OL,20,F"ruined my life and my teammates life."
