OL,3,CUK Athletics boss defends shock
OL,4,Cdecision to include CJ Ujah in GB
OL,5,Crelay squad
OL,7,FThe decision has been down to Darren
OL,8,FCampbell, the UKA's sprint coach to
OL,9,Fbroker peace among the squad, which
OL,10,Falso includes other Tokyo silver
OL,11,Fmedalists Zharnel Hughes and Nethaneel
OL,12,FMitchell-Blake.
OL,14,FMr Buckner said: "Darren Campbell has
OL,15,Fdone a really amazing job in having
OL,16,Flots of really difficult conversations
OL,17,Fwith everyone involved.
OL,26,@vD@ROU
