OL,3,CUK Athletics boss defends shock
OL,4,Cdecision to include CJ Ujah in GB
OL,5,Crelay squad
OL,7,F"The fact that if you look at the
OL,8,Fsquad they are all out there in the
OL,9,FBahamas together and the fact that
OL,10,Fthey are all going out there together
OL,11,Findicates they are prepared to work
OL,12,Fthrough this.
OL,14,F"Richard Kilty is a great athlete,
OL,15,Fthere are lots of strong personalities
OL,16,Fand they are going out and prepping as
OL,17,Fa team and I just think it's a
OL,18,Ftremendous effort by Darren and a
OL,19,Ftribute to them as individuals.
